headline: TKO Extends Exclusive Partnership With T-Mobile Arena Solidifying Las Vegas’ Premier Venue as Official Home
summary: LAS VEGAS, September 03, 2025--TKO and T-Mobile Arena announced the extension of their multi-year partnership establishing the venue as Las Vegas' official home for the UFC and WWE
